Privacy Policy
Developer/Entity:
This app is available for free with ad support and is intended for use as it is.
Purpose
This privacy policy outlines our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use the service.
Information Collection and Use
We do not collect or share personal data directly. However, for a better user experience, the app may collect certain information through third-party services. These services may collect:
Your
IP address
Device information
(such as device name, operating system, etc.)
Usage data
(e.g., app interactions, crash reports)
This information is used to provide and improve the service, as well as for analytics and ad-serving purposes.
Third-Party Services
We use third-party services, including ad networks and analytics providers, which may collect and use information from your device. These services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.
Some third-party services used include but are not limited to:
Ad networks
Analytics tools
Cookies
While this app does not explicitly use cookies, some third-party services integrated with the app may use cookies to collect information and enhance user experiences.
Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information, but no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.
Childrenâ€™s Privacy
This service is not directed to anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age. If we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we will take immediate steps to delete it.
Data Retention and Deletion
We do not retain personal information beyond the purposes described in this policy. If you wish to delete any collected data or have any questions about how your data is handled, please contact us.
Changes to This Policy
We may update our privacy policy from time to time. Users are encouraged to review this page periodically for any changes. Changes are effective immediately after being posted on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us at the email provided in the app's listing.
This policy is effective as of August 27, 2024.